Title: Milwaukee drill bit 7 x 160mm
Description: With three offset aggressive power breakers, this Milwaukee SDS Plus 7mm two-cut drill bit creates a demolition effect, producing micro-cracks in the drilled material. Up to 25x faster, this bit has a centring tip for immediate and highly accurate spot drilling with no risk of skidding on smooth surfaces. The bit's enlarged rebar chamfers prevents side tip damage when hitting rebar, reducing the the risk of jamming while a tapered shoulder design reduces friction, ideal for cordless hammers. The bit's reinforced flute with high volume flute geometry effectively removes dust and transfers full power to the tip for reduced vibration and less breakages.
